    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;evocation&nbsp;[sonic];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;bard 1, bloodrager 1, inquisitor 1, medium 1, psychic 1, sorcerer/wizard 1, witch 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one creature<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;instantaneous; see text<br>\n      <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Fortitude partial (see text);&nbsp;\n      <strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You unleash a powerful scream, inaudible to all but a single target. The target is dazed for 1 round and takes 1d6 points of sonic damage per two caster levels (maximum 5d6). A successful save negates the daze effect and halves the damage.</p>\n</div>\n",
